01:09:55.250 --> 01:09:57.950
[musik meresahkan]

01:10:11.660 --> 01:10:13.580
[suara bisikan]

01:10:17.790 --> 01:10:19.080
[ketukan di pintu]

01:10:19.160 --> 01:10:21.000
- [Sandra] Sayang. - [berdesah]

01:10:22.200 --> 01:10:23.910
Ada apa, Sayang?

01:10:24.000 --> 01:10:25.700
Aku mau berenang.

01:10:25.790 --> 01:10:26.950
Kau mau ikut?

01:10:27.620 --> 01:10:30.750
Tidak usah. Aku sudah mandi. Kau saja.

01:10:30.830 --> 01:10:33.660
Begitu ya? Baiklah, aku berenang ya?

01:10:33.750 --> 01:10:35.500
