Bali dengan kalung itu,

01:19:39.410 --> 01:19:43.290
ilmu pengeleakan Nenek bangkit lagi.

01:19:45.080 --> 01:19:47.250
Sekarang harus bagaimana, Jero?

01:19:48.250 --> 01:19:52.160
Kita harus segera menemukan
jimat itu malam ini juga,

01:19:52.250 --> 01:19:54.000
lalu membakarnya.

01:19:54.620 --> 01:19:56.750
Jangan sampai lewat tengah malam

01:19:57.330 --> 01:20:00.580
agar tidak terjadi korban.

01:20:01.660 --> 01:20:03.700
Di mana kau membuangnya?

01:20:03.790 --> 01:20:05.370
Di semak-semak di depan vila.

01:20:06.330 --> 01:20:08.910
Ayo, segera cari kalung itu.

01:20:09.540 --> 01:20:11.910
Aku akan bantu dengan dupa ini.

01:20:12.580 --> 01:20:14.410
Segera cari kalung itu!

01:20:23.410 --> 01:20:25.910
[musik gamelan]

01:20:31.250 --> 01:20:32.250
[Sandra] Sayang.

01:20:33.330 --> 01:20:35.290
Di mana kau membuangnya?

01:20:35.910 --> 01:20:38.790
Seharusnya ada di sini,
tapi kenapa tidak ada?

01:20:41.290 --> 01:20:44.950
Sebaiknya kita berpencar
agar lebih cepat ketemu.

01:20:45.040 --> 01:20:46.040
Ya.

01:21:36.160 --> 01:21:38.450
[musik menyentak]

01:23:03.500 --> 01:23:04.500
[terkesiap]

01:23:28.700 --> 01:23:33.200
Jimat itu telah ditemukan.

01:23:33.950 --> 01:23:35.160
Sayang.

01:23:35.250 --> 01:23:37.790
[musik lembut]

01:23:42.000 --> 01:23:43.000
[Jero] Ingat,

01:23:44.290 --> 01:23:48.330
yang membakar jimat itu harus
salah satu dari keluarga Nenek.

01:23:49.580 --> 01:23:52.580
Pikirannya tidak boleh kosong.

01:23:53.290 --> 01:23:55.000
Ayo bakar jimat itu.

01:23:57.000 --> 01:24:00.250
Ingat, pikiran jangan sampai kosong.

01:24:12.040 --> 01:24:13.620
[suara bisikan]

01:24:20.500 --> 01:24:22.370
[suara geraman]

01:24:24.120 --> 01:24:26.950
[musik gamelan]

01:24:30.160 --> 01:24:32.580
- [wanita mengerang] - [wanita] Lampu.

01:24:41.870 --> 01:24:43.450
[wanita lanjut mengerang]

01:24:45.120 --> 01:24:46.950
[pria] Hei, bangun.

01:24:48.500 --> 01:24:49.870
[wanita mengerang]

01:24:56.870 --> 01:24:58.290
[wanita mengerang]

01:24:59.580 --> 01:25:01.700
[suara menyeramkan]

01:25:26.330 --> 01:25:27.830
[dialog samar]

01:25:40.080 --> 01:25:41.330
[pria] Cepat!

01:25:44.040 --> 01:25:46.120
[dialog samar]

01:25:47.950 --> 01:25:50.120
[wanita] Jika takut, ke atas saja.

01:26:04.200 --> 01:26:07.200
[pria] Hei.

01:26:08.950 --> 01:26:10.370
[pria] Siap.

01:26:16.700 --> 01:26:19.080
Hei, bangun.

01:26:19.160 --> 01:26:20.410
Bangun.

01:26:21.790 --> 01:26:22.790
[dialog samar]

01:26:22.870 --> 01:26:26.250
[wanita] Bawalah. Bawa batu nisannya.

01:26:28.160 --> 01:26:30.700
Bawa saja ini. Di mana batu nisannya?

01:26:50.370 --> 01:26:52.120
[orang berteriak]

01:27:03.000 --> 01:27:04.790
[dialog samar]

01:27:10.250 --> 01:27:13.000
[orang tertawa]

01:27:13.080 --> 01:27:14.450
[wanita] Ya.

01:27:17.950 --> 01:27:19.500
Akhirnya, aku bisa bicara.

01:27:19.580 --> 01:27:21.226
Waktu itu yang sariawan
di atas, sekarang di bawah.

01:27:21.250 --> 01:27:23.160
Dia marah-marah.

01:27:25.040 --> 01:27:28.370
[musik meresahkan]

01:27:44.950 --> 01:27:45.950
Erik?

01:27:47.410 --> 01:27:48.410
Erik.

01:27:48.950 --> 01:27:50.410
Mau ke mana kau?

01:27:51.330 --> 01:27:52.330
Erik?

01:27:52.870 --> 01:27:53.870
Gendut!

01:28:03.700 --> 01:28:05.200
[berteriak]

01:28:08.750 --> 01:28:09.870
[Denny tercekat]

01:28:14.250 --> 01:28:15.500
[terbatuk]

01:28:27.290 --> 01:28:29.620
[musik berhenti]